## [1.8.1] - 2024-11-13

- Added an authentication mode selector for SMTP profiles with support for password-less (trusted relay) connections.
- Skipped username/password validation when authentication is set to none.
- Mailer now disables SMTP authentication and clears credentials for password-less profiles.

## [1.8.0] - 2024-11-12
- Initial public release with SMTP profile management, queuing, retries, and logging.
